results.name: a(n) = prime digit in A092621(n).
comment: From first 12000 terms, numbers of 2s, 3s, 5s, and 7s are:  2308, 3729, 2267, 3696. Note that numbers of 2s and 5s are very close to each other, and the same is for numbers of 3s and 7s.
results.author: _Zak Seidov_, Mar 09 2014
